					href='https://forms.gle/1Jtfi7Fh4iee7Qv29'
					target='_blank'
					rel='noopener'
					class='font-medium text-blue-500 underline'
					>Envía tu charla
				</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div
			class='mx-auto space-y-16 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-16 sm:space-y-0 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:max-w-5xl'
